my vimd configure

How to use?
git clone https://github.com/VundleVim/Vundle.vim.git ~/.vim/bundle/Vundle.vim
vim : PluginInstall
....
enjoy!

note:
syntastic插件是一个语法检错插件，非常的好用
如何解决syntestic找不到工程头文件的问题?
需要在工程文件夹根目录下创建一个和
let g:syntastic_cpp_config_file = '.include_file'同名的文件,比如.include_file
在配置文件中添加头文件的目录，每个目录占一行比如:
-I/home/**/myproject
-I/home/**/myproject/include
-I/home/**/myproject/include/dir1
